[info] Activation of plug-in SEC Inline Transforms successful, version 19.2. - transforms/SEC

[DQC.US.0167.10100] In the statement 003 - Statement - Statements of Operations (Unaudited) the filer has defined multiple roots calculation elements that do not have a valid calculation tree defined. The root element NetIncomeLoss has sibling root elements of us-gaap:OperatingIncomeLoss, us-gaap:OtherNonoperatingIncome in the filing. The sibling element us-gaap:OperatingIncomeLoss, us-gaap:OtherNonoperatingIncome should appear as a calculation descendant of NetIncomeLoss. This sibling element(s) are defined as calculation descendants in the US GAAP taxonomy.
